# LifeOS — Guardrails & Conventions

## What NOT to Build in MVP (strictly deferred)

If asked to build any of these, decline and note it's a future phase:

| Feature | Why deferred | Future home |
|---------|-------------|-------------|
| IdeaBox research agent | Separate app, different lifecycle | IdeaBox app (ennoble.ai) |
| MedTracker family/caregiver loop | Safety-critical, separate product | MedTracker app |
| Finance analysis or investment advice | Phase 2 | Finance OS plugin |
| Travel / trek planning agent | Phase 2 | Travel Agent plugin |
| Multi-user accounts / teams | Phase 2 | Platform layer |
| Sharing / delegation | Phase 2 | Platform layer |
| Social features | Not in scope ever for core | N/A |
| iOS build | After Android validated | Same codebase, just EAS |
| Home screen widget | Week 4 only, after core works | expo-widgets |
| On-device LLM | Nice to have, complex | Phase 2 upgrade |

