## Environmental Responsibility

- **Default to Haiku.** Only escalate to Sonnet on explicit user request.
- **No background AI polling.** AI fires on user action or scheduled cron only.
- **Batch non-urgent jobs** (spaced rep updates, anti-entropy) in pg_cron at off-peak.
- **Choose green Supabase region** — EU West (Ireland) has cleaner energy than ap-southeast.
- **Never add telemetry that sends data to third parties** without user awareness.

