## Code Quality Checklist (before marking any task done)

- [ ] TypeScript compiles with no errors (`npx tsc --noEmit`)
- [ ] No hardcoded domain strings (use DOMAINS constant)
- [ ] Async functions have try/catch
- [ ] No console.log in code that touches health/medicine/personal data
- [ ] RLS policies tested (verify a second user cannot read first user's data)
- [ ] Offline path tested (airplane mode on device)
- [ ] Push notification tested on real Android device (not simulator)
